CHAPTER 4, DIVISION 1, TITLE 1 OF THE COMMONWEALTH CODE:
1 SECTION 1. PURPOSE.
2 The purpose of this Act is to appropriate local funds from the revenues collected pursuant to
3 Saipan Local Law 11-2 (poker fees).
