6 pursuant to funds allocated to the Third Senatorial District the Saipan and Northern Islands
7 Legislative Delegation (SNILD) hereby appropriates $2,500,000.00 of the revenues collected
8 pursuant to Saipan Local Law 11-2 as amended as follows:
9 (A) $1,700,000.00 to Saipan Higher Education Financial Assistance (SHEFA), provided
10 however that $250,000 of the $1,700,000.00 shall be reserved for SHEFA personnel and

